parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the HVAC servo motor can cause the heating, ventilation, and air conditioning system to malfunction, leading to discomfort and potential safety issues.
symptoms: Inconsistent or lack of airflow
temperature control issues
unusual noises from the HVAC system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the all-wheel drive system can cause loss of traction, reduced vehicle control, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Warning lights or messages indicating all-wheel drive system issues
loss of power or traction
unusual noises or vibrations from the drivetrain.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Parking Brake and Cruise Control Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the parking brake and cruise control systems can cause safety concerns, as the parking brake may become disabled, and the cruise control may not function properly, leading to potential accidents.
symptoms: Intermittent warning lights or messages indicating parking brake and cruise control malfunctions
parking brake failure to engage or disengage
cruise control system failure to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure to Engage Parking Gear
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission to engage parking gear can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle does not lock into park gear
the transmission does not engage parking gear even when the shift lever is in the "P" position
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly when parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handle can cause difficulty or impossibility in opening or closing the door, which can lead to inconvenience, injury, or entrapment.
symptoms: The door handle does not function
the door handle is broken
the door cannot be opened or closed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected shattering of the sunroof glass can cause distraction, loss of control, or accidents, and may lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The sunroof glass shatters suddenly and without warning
the sunroof glass explodes while driving
glass fragments fall into the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty brake actuator can cause the vehicle to fail to stop suddenly, which is a significant safety issue. The brake actuator failure can also lead to a loud, unbearable "brake squawk" noise when the brake pedal is applied.
symptoms: The vehicle makes a loud
unbearable "brake squawk" noise when the brake pedal is applied
the noise is intermittent and increases in loudness over time
the brakes work fine despite the noise.
